      "content": "idk im just really over the side effects and i hate calling my doctor for every little thing like this. wouldn't it be safer to just ease into it? like if i take the st johns wort at the same time as my sertraline for a week or two, wouldn't that help bridge the gap so i don't get withdrawal or anything? i just wanna get the zoloft out of my system as fast as possible so i can feel normal again.",
